data.description: Great opportunity to own this 4-bed, 2-bath home in Maybrook, NY! This cozy property boasts a spacious living area and an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The location is perfect for convenience and commuters as family parks and shopping centers are nearby, along with Highway 84, the NYS thruway, and everything the Hudson Valley offers, such as restaurants, wineries, hiking trails, and much more. Only 60-70 minutes north of NYC! Call today to schedule a private showing! This property is being sold as-is.
